# POA&M Management Engine

## Purpose

Track remediation activities from discovery through validation while maintaining audit-ready documentation.

---

## Inputs

- Failed Controls
- Risk Register
- Vulnerability Findings
- Audit Results
- Manual Exceptions

---

## Processing

- Generate POA&M entries.
- Assign ownership.
- Calculate due dates.
- Monitor remediation progress.
- Validate completed actions.

---

## Outputs

- POA&M Workbook
- Milestone Tracking
- Remediation Reports
- Audit Evidence

---

